data.description: Welcome home to this renovated brick ranch home in the Perl Mack neighborhood. NO HOA. This cozy home features a new coffee bar in kitchen, updated plumbing with copper piping. The beautiful plank wood floors welcome you as you enter and continue through the kitchen. There are refinished hardwoods, new windows and ceiling fans in the 2 main floor bedrooms. New attic insulation, and new lighting throughout. A new electrical panel was purchased and installed and ready to be hooked up. There's a new water heater and new flooring in the basement and a whole house water filter with pressure regulator. The front porch and driveway concrete was recently poured. There is an extra backroom attached to the home but the square footage isn't included in listing. The basement has one bedroom and one nonconforming bedroom with ¾ bath, finished family room, large laundry room with plenty of storage. The backyard features a large shed with loft that can be converted to an ADU, work shop or art studio. Close to light rail, bus routes, highway, shopping, restaurants and parks.
